"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Algorithm for the testing and treatment for hereditary hemochromatosis",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 588px; height: 470px; background-image: url(data:image/gif;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    An algorithm can provide some further direction regarding testing and treatment for HH. The algorithm is modified from the version used in the previous AASLD guidelines. For screening purposes, the serum ferritin is considered elevated if it is &gt;200 ng/mL in men or &gt;150 ng/mL in women.",
